data.description:
Price Reduced from $129,900 to $124,900!!! 
Your heart will be captivated with this cozy 2/2/2 on a beautiful fresh water canal. Live the Florida Lifestyle in the Moorings Community located in the County seat of Citrus County. This lovely abode is filled with cheery colors and spacious bedrooms to entertain friends and family. Enjoy lovely sunsets as you gaze out your enclosed lanai area to the beautiful fresh water canal. Adventurous? Enjoy a stroll or birdwatching from your back yard. Go to the close by community pool, play shuffle board, BBQ's get together, nature trail, and boat ramp to main lake. A great community and all it needs is you! 2007 HVAC, 2009 Roof.
